title: HBO.Boxing.Ricky.Hitman.Hatton.vs.Floyd.Money.Mayweather.[Lloyd]
description:
The one you've been waiting for way too long... The classic HBO Full Rip of Ricky the Hitman Hatton vs Pound for Pound King, Pretty Boy Floyd aka Money Mayweather....

The fight is aptly named "Undefeated" They are two of the best and most exciting fighters in the sport today. With a combined record of 81-0, pound-for-pound king of the ring and world welterweight champion "Pretty Boy" Floyd Mayweather will meet British icon and universally recognized world junior welterweight champion Ricky "The Hitman" Hatton for the world welterweight championship. 

Regardless of one's opinion, when Mayweather and Hatton step into the ring on Dec. 8, it will be a bout destined for the history books and an early Christmas present for fight fans.
